cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG 

This paper focuses on facial expression recognition using 3D face scans, which involves computer vision and graphics techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves 3D modeling and graphics, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
